---
title: Say hi!
nav: contact
description: So you wanna get in touch, eh? Here’s how&hellip;
---

<section class="group group--centered cols">
  <div class="col">
    <h1 class="h--alpha">Hi!</h1>
    <p class="p--alpha">Get in touch about anything, and everything.</p>
    <p>I don’t do YouTube work anymore, but you can read about that <%= link_to "in my journal", "/journal/youtube/", :title => "Read about why I don’t work on YouTube anymore" %>.</p>
    <p>If you’re looking for my employment and education history, you can read all about that in <%= link_to "my CV", "/curriculum-vitae", :title => "Read my curriculum vitae" %>.</p>
  </div>
  <% data.contact.contact.each do |contact| %>
    <div class="col col--break col--break--<%= contact.title.to_slug %>">
      <h2 class="h--beta"><%= contact.title %></h2>
      <p><em><%= contact.when %></em></p>
      <%= contact.desc %>
      <p>
        <%= link_to contact.link.text, contact.link.href, :title => contact.link.title, :class => "btn" %>
      </p>
    </div>
  <% end %>
</section>